track_notes: First drive your car to the first summit Crete de la Madone, there is a lot of room to park and you can visit the Church by the way. From this place go down the hill and follow the path until you have to go inside the forest, use of GPS is recommended! On your way back to the Crete de La Madone , you will be able to activate the second summit!!! very hot in summertime.
You must drive to the hameau de la Vilette, where few people live. The walk is easy and fine; in summer you must get some water. behave the sheep and the guard dogs.
track_title: From south 760m up only. Not 2000m as seen

track_notes: Park at La Mescla, then go to le Reveston. the place is nice with nice panorama and lot of room for antenna
You can also activate the Collet dHuesti
